OL,3,CHotel tycoon unveils rival Heathrow
OL,4,Cexpansion plan with shorter third
OL,5,Crunway
OL,7,FBuilding a 2,800-metre third runway
OL,8,Finstead of the full-length 3,500-metre
OL,9,Frunway planned by the airport would
OL,10,Fresult in "reduced risk" and avoid
OL,11,F"spiralling cost", the company said.
OL,13,FA shorter runway could have limits on
OL,14,Fits use, although Arora Group insisted
OL,15,Fit would be able to accommodate
OL,16,Faircraft of all sizes.
