OL,3,CHotel tycoon unveils rival Heathrow
OL,4,Cexpansion plan with shorter third
OL,5,Crunway
OL,7,FArora Group's Heathrow West proposal
OL,8,Fstates the new runway could be fully
OL,9,Foperational by 2035, while a new
OL,10,Fterminal would open in two phases, in
OL,11,F2036 and 2040.
OL,13,FThe plan, developed with
OL,14,Finfrastructure company Bechtel, has a
OL,15,Fcost estimate of under #25 billion,
OL,16,Fnot including the redevelopment of the
OL,17,Fairport's existing central area.
