OL,3,CHotel tycoon unveils rival Heathrow
OL,4,Cexpansion plan with shorter third
OL,5,Crunway
OL,7,FMr Arora, who is one of the largest
OL,8,Flandowners at Heathrow, said: "After a
OL,9,Fdecade working with our world-leading
OL,10,Fdesign and delivery team, I am very
OL,11,Fproud that the Arora Group can finally
OL,12,Funveil to the UK Government our
OL,13,FHeathrow West proposal, which directly
OL,14,Fmeets and supports the United
OL,15,FKingdom's primary objective of
OL,16,Funlocking economic growth at the UK's
OL,17,Fonly hub airport, with a strong
OL,18,Fcommitment of doing so on-budget and
OL,19,Fon-time.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
