OL,3,CHotel tycoon unveils rival Heathrow
OL,4,Cexpansion plan with shorter third
OL,5,Crunway
OL,7,F"The Arora Group has a proven track
OL,8,Frecord of delivering on-time and on-
OL,9,Fbudget projects including in and
OL,10,Faround Heathrow airport.
OL,12,F"We are delighted that the Government
OL,13,Fhas taken a common-sense approach to
OL,14,Finvite proposals from all interested
OL,15,Fparties for the very first time rather
OL,16,Fthan granting exclusivity to the
OL,17,Fcurrent airport operator, no matter
OL,18,Fits track record."
OL,20,FMr Arora has repeatedly accused the
OL,21,Fairport of wasting money.
