OL,3,CHotel tycoon unveils rival Heathrow
OL,4,Cexpansion plan with shorter third
OL,5,Crunway
OL,7,FIn December 2024, French company
OL,8,FArdian completed a deal to become
OL,9,FHeathrow's largest shareholder with a
OL,10,F23% stake, while Saudi Arabia's
OL,11,Fsovereign wealth fund purchased a 15%
OL,12,Fshare.
OL,14,FChancellor Rachel Reeves gave her
OL,15,Fbacking for a third runway in a speech
OL,16,Fon growth in January.
OL,18,FHeathrow will submit its own expansion
OL,19,Fplan to the Government on Thursday.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
