OL,7,FTransport Secretary Heidi Alexander
OL,8,Fwill then review the Airports National
OL,9,FPolicy Statement, which provides the
OL,10,Fbasis for decision-making on any
OL,11,FDevelopment Consent Order application.
OL,13,FHeathrow is understood to be open to a
OL,14,Fdiscussion with airlines about
OL,15,Fbuilding a shorter runway if it can
OL,16,Fdeliver the same benefits.
OL,18,FThe airport declined to comment on the
OL,19,FArora Group's proposal.
